    • getWSWRLVariable

      WSWRLVariable getWSWRLVariable(org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.IRI iri, WSWRLVariableDomain domain)
      Returns the instance of a variable that corresponds to an IRI. If no variable exists for that IRI, a new instance will be created. Otherwise it returns the instance.
      Parameters:
      iri - Variable IRI.
      domain - Variable domain.
      Returns:
      The variable instance.

    • getWSWRLRule

      WSWRLRule getWSWRLRule(String ruleName, Set<WSWRLAtom> head, Set<WSWRLAtom> body, boolean enabled) throws MissingRankException
      Parameters:
      ruleName - The rule name.
      head - List of the head WSWRLAtom.
      body - List of the body WSWRLAtom.
      enabled - True if the rule is enabled, False otherwise.
      Returns:
      A new WSWRLRule.
      Throws:
      MissingRankException

    • getWSWRLBuiltInAtom

      WSWRLBuiltInAtom getWSWRLBuiltInAtom(String ruleName, org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.IRI builtInIRI, String builtInPrefixedName, List<WSWRLDVariable> variables, WSWRLOntology ontology)
      Parameters:
